OL,7,FManchester Arena bomb plotter Hashem
OL,8,FAbedi has pleaded not guilty to
OL,9,Fcarrying out "terrorist" attacks on
OL,10,Fprison officers at a maximum security
OL,11,Fjail with hot cooking oil and
OL,12,Fmakeshift weapons.
OL,14,FThe 28-year-old defendant appeared at
OL,15,Fthe Old Bailey on Friday by video-link
OL,16,Ffrom Belmarsh jail in south London
OL,17,Fflanked by four prison officers.
