OL,7,FOutlining the allegations, Prosecutor
OL,8,FJocelyn Ledward KC said: "This case
OL,9,Fconcerns an incident on April 12 2025
OL,10,Fat HMP Frankland when Mr Abedi was
OL,11,Fbeing detained.
OL,13,F"During the course of a session where
OL,14,Fhe was permitted to use cooking
OL,15,Fequipment he attacked and attempted to
OL,16,Fmurder three prison officers using hot
OL,17,Foil and makeshift weapons he had
OL,18,Fconstructed himself. He also assaulted
OL,19,Fa fourth prison officer."
