OL,7,FThe court was told that during the
OL,8,Fattack, Abedi shouted out "Allahu
OL,9,Fakbar" twice.
OL,11,FMs Ledward said there was no
OL,12,Findication the defendant had any
OL,13,Fprevious hostility or grievance
OL,14,Ftowards the victims.
OL,16,FShe alleged the defendant held an
OL,17,Fextremist mindset ` "not least his
OL,18,Fconviction in 2020 in connection with
OL,19,Fthe Manchester Arena bombing".
