OL,7,FAbedi went on to plead not guilty to
OL,8,Fthe attempted murders of prison
OL,9,Fofficers Paul Crampton, Gary Speight,
OL,10,Fand Catherine Herbert.
OL,12,FHe denied assaulting a fourth prison
OL,13,Fofficer, Craig Thompson, occasioning
OL,14,Fhim actual bodily harm.
OL,16,FHe pleaded not guilty to possession of
OL,17,Fa bladed or sharply pointed article,
OL,18,Fnamely a knife, inside HMP Frankland
OL,19,Fin County Durham on April 12.
