OL,7,FMrs Justice Cheema-Grubb said Abedi's
OL,8,Ftrial would take place from January 18
OL,9,F2027 and go on for two to three weeks.
OL,11,FShe ordered him to attend his next
OL,12,Fhearing on January 30 2026.
OL,14,FAbedi was not represented by a lawyer
OL,15,Fin court, which Mrs Justice Cheema-
OL,16,FGrubb observed was his choice.
OL,18,FAsked if he wanted to be represented,
OL,19,FAbedi said: "Yeah, basically I don't
OL,20,Fwant to attend anyway. That's why."
