OL,7,FThe defendant was remanded into
OL,8,Fcustody.
OL,10,FAbedi was convicted of assisting with
OL,11,Fthe Manchester terror plot, in which
OL,12,Fhis brother, suicide bomber Salman
OL,13,FAbedi, killed 22 people by detonating
OL,14,Fa homemade rucksack bomb among a crowd
OL,15,Fof concert-goers in May 2017.
OL,17,FHe was jailed for life with a record-
OL,18,Fbreaking 55-year minimum term in
OL,19,FAugust 2020.
